LETS TALK ABOUT IT the weird beginning and the sudden ending to Krishna’s life by his own followers.

episodes.title: How to know you’re in a Toxic relationship 💔
episodes.description: I am not an expert in psychology BUT I did take some classes AND I grew up in a cult surrounded with toxic behaviors and now that I have been out 9 years, I am very well aware of what was toxic and what is healthy and would LOVE to share what I have learned with you and I LOVE to hear what you all have learned in your life experience as well💕 leave it in the comments on my YouTube! Love you guys and I really hope this podcast can help in some way💕 remember to KNOW YOUR WORTH and just because someone else does not value you DOES NOT mean you are not valuable!!!

episodes.title: Michelle/Ava
episodes.description: Trigger warning! There is a lot of talk of abuse in this episode that may be very triggering…we discuss sexual abuse, marital rape etc. please do not listen if this will trigger you. I am very glad we were able to discuss these things and feel healthy enough mentally process them…there was a time where I would have a panic attack trying to explain my abuse and for anyone who is struggling with this and is a minor in the order 801-253-5720 is a number to Utah Sandy DCFS you can call and make an anonymous report if you or someone you know is a minor being sexually abused.
